
Bloodfist Help:  Draelok the Blacksmith

  Draelok is the guilds blacksmith and serves many purposes
within the guild.  He is able to repair and sharpen weapons
for a fee if they should become dull or break.
  He also sells several pieces of equipment which you may find
useful throughout your journey.  Seek him out for a 'list' of
all the things that you may 'buy' if you feel it suits you.
  One of his greatest abilities is the ability to 'forge' your
weapon so you can socket it once you have achieved this ability.
